{"tid":149805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江澤民一罵成名　張寶華：沒有線就沒今天的我","createTime":"2017-03-09T13:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T16:51:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef08cd6b5d14eb269d86b36e9f765549656dd341","tid":149805,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489065467_09d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489065467_09d0.jpg&h=8ddd0278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞可以說是有線電視的「靈魂」，多年來有不少經典報道，其中記者張寶華在2000年，當面問時任國家主席江澤民，是否「欽點」董建華連任特首，遭江澤民怒斥：「too simple，sometimes naive」，被視是本地新聞史的經典場面。<br />\n<br />\n已離開有線及新聞界的張寶華今晚在fb留言表示，有線電視或關門的消息「來得太突然」，她看到新聞後，聯絡新聞部舊上司趙應春，獲覆「生死有命」。<br />\n<br />\n張寶華在有線電視任職近8年，她自言「所有嘅見識」，都是來自在有線的8年裏，表示很感謝有線新聞台給予的機會，「讓我跑遍全世界，亦都跑遍中國大小城市，沒有有線嘅日子就沒有今天的我。」形容「娘家」要結業，感到很難過，指有線新聞部主管一直為下屬「頂住好多壓力」，讓大家有最大空間報道新聞，希望九倉可以為員工作最好的安排。"},{"pid":"b1cf4085354ace90e64ce74cd82ac4900762c374","tid":149805,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56407160&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56407160%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170309&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=41ccca8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56407160%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170309&h=5aa480fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56407160&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170309</a>"},{"pid":"225e7b18c3f74c7ad709108eff5fd8fd3b7e7e20","tid":149805,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score